The group of companies sees the basis of its activities in the dynamic and comprehensive development of the enterprise, the effective use of material resources and the maximum possible protection of the environment for future generations.
To this end, the company has made the following commitments:
• Expect compliance with all international and domestic environmental standards;
• Reducing environmental pollution by saving material resources;
• Improving at all stages of production processes and reducing energy consumption;
• Continuous improvement of the company's environmental protection activities;
• Development of a plan of preventive measures to prevent environmental pollution;
• Continuous monitoring of the situation on labor protection and industrial safety, continuous improvement of the situation in this area;
• Create safe working conditions in its production areas, compliance with occupational safety and health standards in this area;
• Involve all employees in "occupational safety" and "environmental protection" and achieve continuous improvement in this area;
• The main mechanisms envisaged by the enterprise in the implementation of environmental policy.
• Communicate the essence of environmental policy to all employees;
• Evaluate all initiatives to protect the environment and the environment;
• Achieve continuous increase of environmental awareness of staff;
• Rewarding creative initiatives on material saving, energy saving, application of new technologies;
• Environmental certification of manufactured products;
• The implementation of environmental policy will always be in the center of attention, as reflected in all the contracts signed by the company.

The complexity of modern production activities requires a comprehensive approach to Environmental Protection and Occupational Safety:
Creating safe working conditions;
Instruct employees on safe work methods;
Ensuring the safety of production equipment;
Security of buildings and facilities;
Providing employees with personal protective equipment;
Creating an optimal work and rest regime;
Periodic review and monitoring.
